'''Tosi-karu''' was a [[Sernpidalian]] goddess.<ref name="CSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref> When the [[Praetorite Vong]] used the [[Yo'gand's Core]] tactic to pull one of [[Sernpidal/Legends|Sernpidal's]] [[Moon/Legends|moons]], [[Dobido]], into the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] in [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]], the Sernpidalians believed this to be the arrival of Tosi-karu, and panicked accordingly and/or prayed in the streets instead of fleeing from the falling moon.

